{
  "stem": "1479.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And again, I'm going to say, from our experience, we never saw him raise a hand or raise his voice in camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was using compassion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not showing it, but there it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Oskar Schindler did unbelievable things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He amassed a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the end, we know also, what did he do with all the money?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He spent all the money saving people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we cannot say that he was just an SS-man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oskar Schindler was remarkable man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He did remarkable things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And towards the end, he was more and more risking his life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yet, he was determined, as much as possible, to save those people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And those who were in Brunnlitz can tell you a lot of things-- how he did it, what he did it-- Can you tell me?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe, number one, that we know the young boy who was the master, making the stamp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he came up-- one thing we must also remember, that Schindler-- whatever he did-- from day number one, he did surround himself with many Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Business people, engineers, the most talented people, they became his confidants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whatever he did achieve, it was done with the advice of our people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But of course, our people couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Schindler did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was a human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In spite of everything, being and drinking with the murderers, he remained a human being, a caring person.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this we cannot forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Brunnlitz, again, although my husband did mention that we could not produce because over there was only the munitions factory.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was assigned immediately to the biggest punch-press, the most complicated machine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In [NON-ENGLISH], I was working by pots and pans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And over day, I became the number one expert to operate the punch-press.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
